lub kaum sab xis: Ob kab uas sib ntsib los ua ib lub ces kaum
kev sib haum xeeb: Zoo tib yam ntawm qhov loj thiab cov duab
ntug: Lub rooj sib tham ntawm ob lub ntsej muag ntawm cov duab peb sab
ntsej muag: Nto dav hlau ntawm cov duab peb-dimensional
sib npaug: Sab uas yog tib qhov ntev
thaum uas tig mus: Ob kab hauv qhov chaw ob sab uas tsis sib ntsib
dav hlau: Ib lub tiaj ob-dimensional nto uas ob-dimensional khoom yuav dag
taw tes: Ib txoj haujlwm tshwj xeeb ntawm kab, dav hlau, lossis hauv qhov chaw
sab: Kab ntu hauv cov duab geometric uas ua rau sab nrauv ntawm cov khoom
vertex: Lub ntsiab lus ntawm ob sab ntawm daim duab ob sab lossis ob sab ntawm daim duab peb sab sib ntsib
lub voj voog: Ib tug ob-dimensional duab nyob rau hauv uas tag nrho cov ntsiab lus ntawm txoj kab nkhaus yog equidistant los ntawm ib qho chaw nruab nrab
daim duab peb sab: Ib daim duab kaw nrog peb sab
duab plaub: Ib daim duab ob sab, kaw, plaub sab nrog plaub sab xis
square: Ib hom tshwj xeeb ntawm cov duab plaub uas muaj qhov sib npaug ntawm sab thiab sib npaug sib npaug
kub: Daim duab peb-dimensional nrog zoo tib yam equilateral squares li ntsej muag
